pokedexEntries.red: Its hard scales provide strong protection. It uses its hefty bulk to execute powerful moves.
pokedexEntries.blue: Its hard scales provide strong protection. It uses its hefty bulk to execute powerful moves.
pokedexEntries.yellow: Tough scales cover the sturdy body of this Pokémon. It appears that the scales grow in cycles.
pokedexEntries.gold: Its body is covered with needle-like scales. It never shows signs of shrinking from any attack.
pokedexEntries.silver: It uses its scaly rugged body to seal the entrance of its nest and protect its young from predators.
pokedexEntries.crystal: The hard scales that cover its strong body serve as excellent protection from any attack.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Nidoqueen's body is encased in extremely hard scales. It is adept at sending foes flying with harsh tackles. This Pokémon is at its strongest when it is defending its young.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Nidoqueen's body is encased in extremely hard scales. It is adept at sending foes flying with harsh tackles. This Pokémon is at its strongest when it is defending its young.
pokedexEntries.emerald: It is adept at sending foes flying with harsh tackles using its tough, scaly body. This Pokémon is at its strongest when it is defending its young.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: The body is covered by stiff, needle-like scales. If it becomes excited, the needles bristle outwards.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: Its hard scales provide strong protection. It uses its hefty bulk to execute powerful moves.
pokedexEntries.diamond: Its entire body is armored with hard scales. It will protect the young in its burrow with its life.
